name: SHARKS
summary:
👑👑 LONG LIVE THE SHARK KING!!👑👑

"The Shark King" is coming to SHARKS! Look out for him next time you're playing, he loves giving out Royal Tokens to unlock free cosmetics and goldfish.

✅ You're a shark
✅ Hang out with friends
✅ Proximity voice chat
✅ Public and Private lobbies/rooms
✅ 100's of cosmetics to express your true shark

🦈 You're a shark: use your mouth to bite, grab, carry, place, build and attack in this multiplayer physics sandbox game. 

🦈 Swim around to collect hidden treasures...
